PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR, namely Associate Chief Justice DAVID HECTOR CAMPBELL of the Supreme Court of British Columbia, who shall temporarily execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of BRITISH COLUMBIA for the period extending from the 3rd to the 15th of July, 1993.
